description: My place is close to Rambling House, Woodlawn Train, Subways, etc..  . You’ll love my place because of the location, convenience, Public transit, close to Bars&Restaurants... . The place is good for couples, solo adventurers, and business travelers.
name: Private Room In Woodlawn :)
review: This place is a modern up to date, I suspect newly refurbished, apartment. No complaints whatsoever. It is quiet at night, the bed is comfortable and I slept well.
